a believer in winning in a way that's honourable.\", \"from\": 2527, \"to\": 2581, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a believer\", \"from\": 2532, \"to\": 2542}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2562}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reaching the finish line first is obviously the main goal.\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2640, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the finish line\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2606}, {\"ngram\": \"the main goal\", \"from\": 2626, \"to\": 2639}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But still I am a big fan in proving myself, not to anybody in particular, but to myself the work I am putting in, it's doing something in a certain way, I am not saying I will do it all the time.\", \"from\": 2641, \"to\": 2836, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a big fan\", \"from\": 2656, \"to\": 2665}, {\"ngram\": \"anybody\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2699}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2775}, {\"ngram\": \"a certain way\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2792}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's about performing as good as you can in the circumstances and how they are.\", \"from\": 2837, \"to\": 2916, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the circumstances\", \"from\": 2881, \"to\": 2898}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just going to continue getting better and winning as much as I can.\\\"\", \"from\": 2917, \"to\": 2990, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ingebrigtsen then elaborated on his desire to win in a certain way and suggested his rivals lacked \\\"confidence\\\" to push the pace in the 5000m to test his strength more than his speed.\", \"from\": 2992, \"to\": 3175, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ingebrigtsen\", \"from\": 2992, \"to\": 3004}, {\"ngram\": \"his desire\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3034}, {\"ngram\": \"a certain way\", \"from\": 3045, \"to\": 3058}, {\"ngram\": \"his rivals\", \"from\": 3073, \"to\": 3083}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"confidence\", \"from\": 3091, \"to\": 3102}, {\"ngram\": \"the pace\", \"from\": 3112, \"to\": 3120}, {\"ngram\": \"the 5000m\", \"from\": 3124, \"to\": 3133}, {\"ngram\": \"his strength\", \"from\": 3142, \"to\": 3154}, {\"ngram\": \"his speed\", \"from\": 3165, \"to\": 3174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's dangerous to go into a championship race expecting anything,\\\" he concluded \\\"It comes down to the athletes and the way they see their chances of getting the best out of themselves.\", \"from\": 3177, \"to\": 3362, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a championship race\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3223}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 3234, \"to\": 3242}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3288}, {\"ngram\": \"their chances\", \"from\": 3310, \"to\": 3323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For some people that might be different to what they think themselves to other people.\", \"from\": 3364, \"to\": 3451, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some people\", \"from\": 3369, \"to\": 3380}, {\"ngram\": \"other people\", \"from\": 3438, \"to\": 3450}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think we were all expecting a somewhat faster race.\", \"from\": 3452, \"to\": 3505, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a somewhat faster race\", \"from\": 3482, \"to\": 3504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it still comes down to everybody's expectations about how they can perform.\", \"from\": 3506, \"to\": 3585, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everybody's expectations\", \"from\": 3533, \"to\": 3557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Some people do not have the confidence to do anything, they are just racing the race as it unfolds.\", \"from\": 3587, \"to\": 3687, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some people\", \"from\": 3588, \"to\": 3599}, {\"ngram\": \"the confidence\", \"from\": 3612, \"to\": 3626}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 3633, \"to\": 3641}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 3664, \"to\": 3672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But some people 